### Post a question as gardener
POST http://localhost:5050/api/questions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "Why are my tomato leaves turning yellow?",
  "content": "I have been growing tomatoes for 3 weeks and the bottom leaves are turning yellow. I water them every other day. Is this normal?",
  "tags": ["tomatoes", "outdoor", "watering"]
}

